Package: NonInfParTren
Type: Package
Title: Test Reduced vs Expanded Model Coefficient Linear Combinations
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-12-06
Authors@: 
  c(person("Alyssa", "Bilinski", email = "alyssa\_bilinski@brown.edu", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "XXX")),
    person("Laura", "Hatfield", email = "hatfield-laura@norc.org", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0366-3929")))
Description: Fits reduced and expanded linear models and tests the difference of a linear combination of parameters from the fitted models using seemingly unrelated regression methods to account for the covariance between models, as described in "Nothing to See Here: A non-inferiority approach to parallel trends" by Alyssa Bilinski and Laura Hatfield.
